    <h2>Offsetting columns</h2>
    <p>Column off sets can be controlled via the <code>o-col-start-[columnStart]</code> class.</p>
    <p>Similar to responsive column classes, offset classes can also be used based according to the <code>$column_breakpoints</code> map variable, with the breakpoint size being before the columnStart value: <code>o-col-start-[breakpoint]-[columnStart]</code></p>
  </div>
</div>

